    {
        "content": "<p>To point out a new feature that will be in the next release, now <code>#eval</code> will attempt to auto-derive <code>Repr</code> instances:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">natural</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">function</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">notation</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">max</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ℕ\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">natural</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">infixr</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">70</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\" ⇒ \"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">function</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Auto-derives a Repr instance!</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⇒</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Tp.function (Tp.natural) (Tp.natural)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>If you happen to have a ToExpr instance, then that will be used instead and it will use the normal pretty printing system:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ToExpr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Tp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">toTypeExpr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">``Tp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">toExpr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">go</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">go</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">``Tp.natural</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⇒</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mkApp2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">``Tp.function</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[])</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">go</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">go</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⇒</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- ℕ ⇒ ℕ</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The output is hoverable in the Infoview:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/aLb8a-BQZpN-qI6roFMyKFsh/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/aLb8a-BQZpN-qI6roFMyKFsh/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"446x86\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/aLb8a-BQZpN-qI6roFMyKFsh/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
        "id": 476649955,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1728867166
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"306601\">@Kyle Miller</span> Thanks for that update. Good to know.</p>",
